dataObject.name:
Description
This process reflects an individual interior configuration of an aircraft. A customer can have many different requirements for the interior of his aircraft and our company has to take these requirements into account in its own process.
- Customer must submit configuration request - Customer must create configuration and send it back to the company - The customer's wishes are passed on to subteams according to their responsibilities - Integration work is carried out at HQ - Test flight must be performed
